ZALTYS-PYTHON-UTILS
===================

Python2/3 utilities for the Zaltys platform.


zaltys_zwire
------------
A python module wrapper for the libzaltys-zwire shared-object library.


zspiread & zspiwrite
--------------------
Shell commands for Zwire SPI reads and writes.


zaltys_smpi_gateway
-------------------
A python module that allows the SMPI bus access mechanism (e.g. Zwire
SPI or PCIe) to be abstracted away from hardware register read/writes.
Thus changing the bus access mechanism will not require changing
higher level source code.


zaltys_ad9361_driver
-------------------
A python module wrapper for the libzaltys-ad9361 shared-object library.


zaltys_hdrmm_driver
-------------------
A pure python driver for the Zaltys HDRM Modulator.


zaltys_hdrmd_driver
-------------------
A python module wrapper for the libzaltys-hdrmd shared-object library.


zaltys_dvbs2m_driver
-------------------
A pure python driver for the Zaltys DVB-S2 Modulator.


zaltys_dvbs2d_driver
-------------------
A python module wrapper for the libzaltys-dvbs2d shared-object library.


zaltys_plsv_utils
-----------------
Utilities for DVB-S2(X) frame properties based on PLS value lookup.


dvbs2_bbframe_test & dvbs2_continuous_test
------------------------------------------
Example code that sends and receives BBFRAMEs via the ZMP003 DVB-S2(X)
modem in loopback configuration.


